Package fr.univtln.ganne882.project2007.gui

Class Summary
AlgosFrame This Frame is accessible from both teachers and students, but teachers have more privileges.
AlgosTab This tab is accessible only for teachers It presents all available algorithms, and an access in order to make modifications
DescriptionTab This tab in the algos frame contents the main attributes of the given algorithm
LoginDialog This is the first class to be instancied : the user first gives his login and password and then he is recognized as a teacher or a student
Main Main executor class
MainFrameStudent When logged, this is the first frame a student will be able to see
MainFrameTeacher When logged, this is the interface a teacher directly accesses to
Messages  
PropositionTab This is the tab where classes can be executed.
StudentsTab The teacher can observe the work of his students
TestsGUI JUnit test cases to test an as long and as usefull lot of tests as possible
